comments: Finney-Smith (DAL) gives a step of distance when establishing himself in Brown's (DEN) path and he absorbs the contact as Brown simultaneously steals the pass.
Dinwiddie (DAL) is turning away from Caldwell-Pope (DEN) and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the driving shot attempt.
Kleber (DAL) initiates contact across Brown's (DEN) right arm during the put-back attempt.
Jokic (DEN) and Kleber (DAL) briefly engage and disengage as they position themselves for a potential rebound and incidental contact occurs.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) establishes himself in Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Doncic (DAL) keeps his hand on the side of the ball in between dribbles.
Murray (DEN) legally contests Doncic's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Finney-Smith (DAL) engages and disengages with Gordon (DEN) after the release of the jump shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) and Doncic (DAL) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Murray (DEN) places two hands on Kleber's (DAL) back with slight extension but the contact is marginal.
Kleber (DAL) firms up over his right foot and absorbs the contact that occurs with Caldwell-Pope (DEN) as the pick is set.
Doncic (DAL) slightly extends his off-arm as Murray (DEN) crowds his space but the contact in the post is marginal and Murray is not dislodged from his defensive position.
Murray (DEN) reaches in and initiates contact with Doncic's (DAL) left arm, affecting Doncic's SQBR and causing him to briefly lose control of the ball.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Jokic (DEN) and Finney-Smith (DAL) engage and disengage with one another off ball in the post.
Finney-Smith (DAL) maintains a rested hand on Jokic's (DEN) side and marginal contact occurs in the post.
Gordon (DEN) grasps and then quickly releases Dinwiddie's (DAL) arm as he sets the screen.
Jokic (DEN) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Dinwiddie (DAL) and Brown (DEN) make incidental foot contact with one another after they each return to the floor following the jump shot attempt.
Wood (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position from a wide stance but Murray (DEN) is able to avoid the contact.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) brings his hands forward as he goes over the pick and marginal contact occurs with Doncic's (DAL) front.
Finney-Smith (DAL) maintains his left foot as his pivot as he starts his dribble.
Powell (DAL) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Powell (DAL) maintains a rested forearm on Jokic's (DEN) side and marginal contact occurs as Jokic moves toward the top of the perimeter.
Finney-Smith (DAL) briefly places a hand on Jokic's (DEN) arm as he goes around the pick, but Jokic raises his own arm into Finney-Smith to draw attention to the marginal contact.
Braun (DEN) and Dinwiddie (DAL) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Braun (DEN) commits a take foul on Dinwiddie (DAL).
Bullock (DAL) commits a take foul on Murray (DEN). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) extends his hand forward and initiates contact with Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) hip, affecting his SQBR along the sideline.
Jokic (DEN) and Kleber (DAL) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Bullock (DAL) immediately slides his hands off of Gordon's (DEN) side and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Gordon (DEN) establishes himself in Bullock's (DAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Bullock (DAL) brushes Murray's (DEN) back as he starts his upward shooting motion and marginal contact occurs during the shot attempt.
